<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ website_title }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        .feature {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }
        .feature h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #ffd700;
        }
        .success-badge {
            background: #27ae60;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .tech-stack {
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .tech-item {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 5px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üöÄ {{ website_title }}</h1>
            <div class="subtitle">{{ welcome_message }}</div>
            
            <div class="success-badge">
                ‚úÖ FULLY AUTOMATED DEVOPS PIPELINE
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tech-stack">
            <div class="tech-item">Terraform</div>
            <div class="tech-item">Ansible</div>
            <div class="tech-item">AWS EC2</div>
            <div class="tech-item">NGINX</div>
            <div class="tech-item">Ubuntu</div>
            <div class="tech-item">SSH</div>
        </div>

        <div class="features">
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>üèóÔ∏è Infrastructure as Code</h3>
                <p>Terraform created all AWS resources: VPC, Subnet, Security Groups, and EC2 instance</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>‚öôÔ∏è Configuration Management</h3>
                <p>Ansible automated software installation, service configuration, and deployment</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>üîí Secure by Design</h3>
                <p>Proper security groups, SSH key authentication, and minimal exposure</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature">
                <h3>üîÑ Repeatable Process</h3>
                <p>Entire environment can be recreated with two simple commands</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info">
            <p><strong>Server:</strong> {{ ansible_hostname }} | <strong>IP:</strong> {{ ansible_default_ipv4.address }}</p>
            <p><strong>Deployed:</strong> {{ ansible_date_time.iso8601 }}</p>
            <p><a href="/info.html" style="color: #ffd700; text-decoration: none;">üìä View Detailed Server Info</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
